reviewText: A must have for anyone interested in the Pacific Theater of operations during WW2. Footage you won't find anywhere else that I'm aware of. It's very well narrated and won't disappoint.
Love the Video.  Recommend very high to anyone to buy and View over and over again.
I luv this!!! (Had to write something)  lol
for the most part this DVD edition has memorable pacific battle scenes. there are time though that this edition loses itself. needs to be better focused
